                <h1>Fixing TV Audio: Hearing Music but No Voices</h1>
                <p>Are you experiencing an issue where you can only hear background music but no voices on your TV? This common problem can be frustrating. Check your audio settings, ensure the audio output is set correctly, and inspect the TV’s balance settings. Sometimes, switching to stereo mode can resolve this issue and restore clear dialogue.</p>
